This is an overview page to point to various pages we have on the topic:



We pay not only attention to technical [[WiFi P2P]] developments, but to the social aspect of trying to build bottom up [[Customer-build network infrastructures]] as evidenced in the [[Wireless Commons]] and [[Personal Telco Movement]], with examples such as [[Fon]], [[Green WiFi]], etc...

See also the coverage of [[WiFi Radio]], which refers to the ability to  receive internet-based radiostations through a WiFi connection [[WiFi Phones]] for [[Voice over WiFi]]reception


